                <p>&nbsp;</p>
              </div>
              <div class="term-input-row">
                <span class="prompt-text">C:\PORK&gt;</span>
                <input type="text" class="term-input" id="term-input" autocomplete="off" spellcheck="false" aria-label="Terminal command input" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="separator">────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────</div>

          <!-- PHOTO ALBUM — Porkbun Pig Through the Ages -->
          <div class="info-card">
            <h3>[ ALBUM.EXE — The Porkbun Pig: A Life in Photos ]</h3>
            <p class="album-subtitle">From dial-up to the metaverse, our pig has seen it all.</p>
            <div class="photo-album">

              <div class="photo-card">
                <div class="photo-era">1995</div>
                <div class="photo-frame polaroid">
                  <pre class="photo-ascii" aria-label="Pig at a computer in 1995">
  ╭──────────────────╮
  │    ╭────╮        │
  │    │◉  ◉│  ┌──┐  │
  │    │ oo │  │::│  │
  │    ╰─┬──╯  │__│  │
  │      │   ╔══════╗│
  │    ╭─┴─╮ ║ AOL  ║│
  │    │   │ ║ v3.0 ║│
  │    ╰───╯ ╚══════╝│
  ╰──────────────────╯</pre>
                  <p class="photo-caption">"You've Got Oink!"</p>
                  <p class="photo-desc">Baby pig discovers the internet via AOL dial-up. Immediately tries to register coolpig.com. It was taken.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="photo-card">
                <div class="photo-era">2001</div>
                <div class="photo-frame polaroid">
