  │  CONSTRUCTION     │
  │    ╭────╮  ⚒     │
  │    │◉  ◉│ /web/  │
  │    │ oo │ ring/   │
  │    ╰─┬──╯ next   │
  │  ♪  ─┤  ♪ ♪     │
  │ [MIDI PLAYS]     │
  │ visitor #000042  │
  ╰──────────────────╯</pre>
                  <p class="photo-caption">"GeoPorkCities"</p>
                  <p class="photo-desc">The pig builds their first website. Features: animated GIF background, auto-playing MIDI, a hit counter, and Comic Sans. Beautiful.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="photo-card">
                <div class="photo-era">2007</div>
                <div class="photo-frame polaroid">
                  <pre class="photo-ascii" aria-label="Pig with early smartphone">
  ╭──────────────────╮
  │     ╭────╮       │
  │     │◉  ◉│ ╭───╮ │
  │     │ oo │ │ 📱│ │
  │     ╰─┬──╯ │top│ │
  │ ╭─────┤    │ 8 │ │
  │ │MyPig│    ╰───╯ │
  │ │Space│          │
  │ │ .com│  *oink*  │
  │ ╰─────╯          │
  ╰──────────────────╯</pre>
