              <div class="photo-card">
                <div class="photo-era">2014</div>
                <div class="photo-frame polaroid">
                  <pre class="photo-ascii" aria-label="Pig founding Porkbun">
  ╭──────────────────╮
  │  ╔══════════════╗│
  │  ║   PORKBUN    ║│
  │  ║  EST. 2014   ║│
  │  ╚══════════════╝│
  │     ╭────╮       │
  │     │◉  ◉│ ♥     │
  │     │ oo │/      │
  │     ╰─┬──╯       │
  │  "domains for    │
  │   everyone!"     │
  ╰──────────────────╯</pre>
                  <p class="photo-caption">"The Porkbun Is Born"</p>
                  <p class="photo-desc">Our pig finds their true calling: making domain registration affordable, simple, and actually fun. The rest is internet history.</p>
                </div>
