  │  ║QUANTUM║ ·    │
  │  ║DOMAINS║      │
  │  ╚═══════╝  ✦   │
  ╰──────────────────╯</pre>
                  <p class="photo-caption">"The Future"</p>
                  <p class="photo-desc">Year 2099: Porkbun now sells quantum domain names across parallel dimensions. Price? Still cheaper than the other guys.</p>
